title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result should be that the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Verify that the query result is stored in the output parameter as an object.
3. Open the data set dialog.
4. Confirm that the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
